5000|$|Many {{people are}} calling for a green <b>national</b> <b>product</b> that would {{indicate}} if activities benefit or harm the economy and well-being. This green <b>national</b> <b>product</b> would revolve around {{the social and economic}} issues on which many green movements have focused: care for the earth and all that sustain it. [...] This new <b>national</b> <b>product</b> would differ from the traditional GNP by addressing both the sustainability and well-being of the planet and its inhabitants. [...] It is essential that this system takes into account natural capital, which is currently hidden from our traditional measurement.|$|R
